🌐 Language Translator

A simple and efficient language translator built to translate text between multiple languages quickly and accurately.

✨ Features

- 🌍 Translate text into multiple languages
- ⚡ Fast and responsive interface
- 🎨 Clean and user-friendly design
- 📱 Works across different devices
- 🔒 Simple and lightweight implementation

🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Translation API

🚀 Getting Started

1. Clone the repository:
   
   git clone https://github.com/your-Abhigya-code/language-translator.git

2. Open the project folder.

3. Run "index.html" in your browser.

